#X text 50 15 In this example we combine keyboard tracking \, envelope and LFO as modulation sources. The modulation amount of each is independent. The envelope and LFO amount are both directly in cents. There's also a [drive~] before the filter and this structure is a very basic subtractive synth. In the end we add some reverb. Of course \, many subtractive synths also incorporate many effects like chorus \, flanging \, delay \, reverb \, etc..., f 66;
